fields.body_template:
Thank you for teaching the workshop at {{ workshop.venue }}!

This workshop slug is {{ workshop.slug }}. (The ‘workshop slug’ is a stand in for being able to generate the survey link in the future, because it’s generated from the slug.)

We want to be sure to give credit to all of our instructors and helpers in our database.

{% if helpers %}We currently have these helpers listed:
{% for helper in helpers %}
* {{ helper }}{% endfor %}

If you have additional helpers, please send us their names and email addresses.
{% else %}
We don’t have the names of any of your helpers. To include them on our website please send us their name and email address.
{% endif %}

Weekly instructors discussion sessions where you can share your feedback and hear from other instructors. Feel free to join us whenever you are available. Check out the calendar <a href="https://pad.carpentries.org/community-discussions">here</a>. Be sure to check your timezone when you sign up.

If you have any questions regarding anything I’ve shared do not hesitate to email me directly. Thanks for all of your hard work running this workshop!

Thanks for all you do!

Best,  
{{ assignee }}
